Rules:
This game can be played for 1-4 people.

To play X-Com: The Board Game you need to either download the app to your mobile (recommended; just search for xcom in Google Play or App Store) or to use the online app available at https://xcomapp.fantasyflightgames.com/web/Player.html

After you get in the App, just select Tutorial.

If you like the game, buy it! It is definitely more fun with friends around you!
